---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Contact - Richad's Blog" description="Get in touch with Richad about mathematics, questions, or collaboration">
	<section class="contact-hero">
		<div class="hero-content">
			<h1 class="hero-title">Let's Connect!</h1>
			<p class="hero-description">
				Have a math question, want to discuss a problem, or just say hello? 
				I'd love to hear from you and connect with fellow math enthusiasts!
			</p>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="contact-content">
		<div class="contact-container">
			<div class="contact-grid">
				<div class="contact-info">
					<h2>Get In Touch</h2>
					<p>
						As a young mathematician, I'm always excited to connect with others who share 
						my passion for learning and problem-solving. Whether you're a student, teacher, 
						or just someone curious about math, I'd love to hear from you!
					</p>

					<div class="contact-methods">
						<div class="contact-method">
							<div class="method-icon">üìß</div>
							<div class="method-info">
								<h3>Email</h3>
								<p>richad.math@example.com</p>
								<span class="method-note">Best for detailed questions or discussions</span>
							</div>
						</div>

						<div class="contact-method">
							<div class="method-icon">üí¨</div>
							<div class="method-info">
								<h3>Math Forums</h3>
								<p>Find me on various math discussion forums</p>
								<span class="method-note">Great for collaborative problem-solving</span>
							</div>
						</div>

						<div class="contact-method">
							<div class="method-icon">üìö</div>
							<div class="method-info">
								<h3>Study Groups</h3>
								<p>Local math study sessions</p>
								<span class="method-note">In-person collaboration when possible</span>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>

					<div class="response-info">
						<h3>Response Time</h3>
						<p>
							I typically respond within 24-48 hours. Please be patient as I balance 
							my studies with blog writing and responding to messages!
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="contact-form-section">
					<form class="contact-form" action="#" method="POST">
						<h2>Send a Message</h2>
						
						<div class="form-group">
							<label for="name">Your Name</label>
							<input type="text" id="name" name="name" required>
						</div>

						<div class="form-group">
							<label for="email">Your Email</label>
							<input type="email" id="email" name="email" required>
						</div>

						<div class="form-group">
							<label for="subject">Subject</label>
							<select id="subject" name="subject" required>
								<option value="">Choose a topic...</option>
								<option value="math-question">Math Question</option>
								<option value="study-help">Study Help</option>
								<option value="blog-feedback">Blog Feedback</option>
								<option value="collaboration">Collaboration</option>
								<option value="general">General Inquiry</option>
							</select>
						</div>

						<div class="form-group">
							<label for="message">Your Message</label>
							<textarea id="message" name="message" rows="6" required placeholder="Tell me about your math question, feedback, or just say hello!"></textarea>
						</div>

						<button type="submit" class="submit-btn">Send Message</button>
					</form>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="faq-section">
		<div class="faq-container">
			<h2 class="section-title">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
			<div class="faq-grid">
				<div class="faq-item">
					<h3>Can you help me with my homework?</h3>
					<p>
						While I can't do your homework for you, I'm happy to help explain concepts, 
						guide you through problem-solving strategies, and point you in the right direction!
					</p>
				</div>

				<div class="faq-item">
					<h3>What math topics do you cover?</h3>
					<p>
						I focus primarily on algebra, geometry, pre-calculus, and some basic calculus. 
						I also enjoy number theory and mathematical problem-solving techniques.
					</p>
				</div>

				<div class="faq-item">
					<h3>Do you offer tutoring?</h3>
					<p>
						Currently, I focus on sharing knowledge through my blog. However, I'm always 
						open to study group collaborations and peer-to-peer learning opportunities.
					</p>
				</div>

				<div class="faq-item">
					<h3>How did you get interested in math?</h3>
					<p>
						Great question! I started getting really interested in math around age 11 when 
						I discovered how elegant and logical mathematical solutions could be. Check out 
						my About page for more details!
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="connect-section">
		<div class="connect-container">
			<h2>Other Ways to Connect</h2>
			<div class="connect-cards">
				<div class="connect-card">
					<div class="connect-icon">üìù</div>
					<h3>Subscribe to Updates</h3>
					<p>Get notified when I publish new blog posts about mathematics and learning.</p>
					<button class="connect-btn">Subscribe</button>
				</div>

				<div class="connect-card">
					<div class="connect-icon">ü§ù</div>
					<h3>Join Study Groups</h3>
					<p>Connect with other young mathematicians for collaborative learning sessions.</p>
					<button class="connect-btn">Learn More</button>
				</div>

				<div class="connect-card">
					<div class="connect-icon">üí°</div>
					<h3>Suggest Topics</h3>
					<p>Have a math topic you'd like me to write about? Let me know your suggestions!</p>
					<button class="connect-btn">Suggest</button>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>
</Layout>

<style>
	.contact-hero {
		padding: 4rem 0;
		background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
		backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
		border-radius: 20px;
		margin-bottom: 4rem;
		text-align: center;
	}

	.hero-title {
		font-size: 3.5rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		color: white;
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
	}

	.hero-description {
		font-size: 1.2rem;
		color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
		max-width: 600px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		line-height: 1.7;
	}

	.contact-content {
		margin-bottom: 4rem;
	}

	.contact-container, .faq-container, .connect-container {
		max-width: 1200px;
		margin: 0 auto;
	}

	.contact-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
		gap: 4rem;
		align-items: start;
	}

	.contact-info h2 {
		font-size: 2rem;
		font-weight: 600;
		color: white;
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
	}

	.contact-info p {
		color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
		line-height: 1.7;
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
	}

	.contact-methods {
		margin-bottom: 3rem;
	}

	.contact-method {
		display: flex;
		align-items: flex-start;
		gap: 1.5rem;
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
		padding: 1.5rem;
		background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
		border-radius: 15px;
	}

	.method-icon {
		font-size: 2rem;
		flex-shrink: 0;
	}

	.method-info h3 {
		color: white;
		font-size: 1.2rem;
		margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
	}

	.method-info p {
		color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
		margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
		margin: 0 0 0.5rem 0;
	}

	.method-note {
		color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);
		font-size: 0.9rem;
		font-style: italic;
	}

	.response-info {
		background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
		padding: 1.5rem;
		border-radius: 15px;
	}

	.response-info h3 {
		color: white;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
	}

	.response-info p {
		margin: 0;
		color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
	}

	.contact-form-section {
		background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
		backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
		padding: 2.5rem;
		border-radius: 20px;
	}

	.contact-form h2 {
		color: white;
		font-size: 2rem;
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
		text-align: center;
	}

	.form-group {
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
	}

	.form-group label {
		display: block;
		color: white;
		font-weight: 500;
		margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
	}

	.form-group input,
	.form-group select,
	.form-group textarea {
		width: 100%;
		padding: 1rem;
		border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
		border-radius: 10px;
		background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
		color: white;
		font-size: 1rem;
		transition: border-color 0.3s ease;
	}

	.form-group input:focus,
	.form-group select:focus,
	.form-group textarea:focus {
		outline: none;
		border-color: #feca57;
	}

	.form-group input::placeholder,
	.form-group textarea::placeholder {
		color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
	}

	.submit-btn {
		width: 100%;
		padding: 1rem 2rem;
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff6b6b 0%, #feca57 100%);
		color: white;
		border: none;
		border-radius: 50px;
		font-size: 1.1rem;
		font-weight: 600;
		cursor: pointer;
		transition: transform 0.3s ease;
	}

	.submit-btn:hover {
		transform: translateY(-2px);
	}

	.faq-section {
		margin-bottom: 4rem;
	}

	.section-title {
		font-size: 2.5rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		text-align: center;
		margin-bottom: 3rem;
		color: white;
	}

	.faq-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
		gap: 2rem;
	}

	.faq-item {
		background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
		backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
		padding: 2rem;
		border-radius: 20px;
	}

	.faq-item h3 {
		color: white;
		font-size: 1.3rem;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
	}

	.faq-item p {
		color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
		line-height: 1.6;
		margin: 0;
	}

	.connect-section {
		background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
		backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
		border-radius: 20px;
		padding: 4rem 2rem;
	}

	.connect-container h2 {
		font-size: 2.5rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		text-align: center;
		margin-bottom: 3rem;
		color: white;
	}

	.connect-cards {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
		gap: 2rem;
	}

	.connect-card {
		background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
		padding: 2rem;
		border-radius: 20px;
		text-align: center;
		transition: transform 0.3s ease;
	}

	.connect-card:hover {
		transform: translateY(-5px);
	}

	.connect-icon {
		font-size: 3rem;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
	}

	.connect-card h3 {
		color: white;
		font-size: 1.3rem;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
	}

	.connect-card p {
		color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
		line-height: 1.6;
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
	}

	.connect-btn {
		padding: 0.8rem 1.5rem;
		background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
		color: white;
		border: 2px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
		border-radius: 25px;
		font-weight: 600;
		cursor: pointer;
		transition: all 0.3s ease;
	}

	.connect-btn:hover {
		background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
		transform: translateY(-2px);
	}

	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		.hero-title {
			font-size: 2.5rem;
		}

		.contact-grid {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
			gap: 2rem;
		}

		.contact-form-section {
			padding: 2rem;
		}

		.section-title {
			font-size: 2rem;
		}

		.connect-section {
			padding: 3rem 1rem;
		}
	}
</style>
